<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/locomotive-scroll@3.5.4/dist/locomotive-scroll.css"
    />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@4.2.0/fonts/remixicon.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../stylesheets/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="main">
      <div id="page1">
        <div id="nav">
          <h1 onclick="redirectToHome()"><img style="height: 5vh; object-fit: cover; object-position: center; width: 13vw;margin-top: 2vh;" src="../images/logo.png" alt=""></h1>
          <div id="navpart-2">
            <h1 id="home" onclick="redirectToHome()">Home</h1>
            <h1 id="about" onclick="redirectToAbout()">About us</h1>
            <h1 id="feeding" onclick="redirectToFeeding()"> Awards and Recognitions</h1>
            <h1 id="milestone" onclick="redirectToMilestone()">Milestones</h1>
            <h1 id="partner" onclick="redirectToPartner()">Partner with Us</h1>
            <h1 id="contact" onclick="redirectToContact()">Contact</h1>
          </div>
          <div id="navpart-3">
            <button
              id="donate"
              style="padding: 1vh 3vw; text-align: center; width: fit-content"
              onclick="redirectToDonate()"
            >
              <i class="ri-heart-fill"></i>Donate
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="hero">
          <div id="left">
            <h1>Food is god</h1>
            <h3>"If you can't feed a hundred people, then feed just one." - Mother Teresa</h3>
          </div>
          <div id="right">
            <img
              src="https://c4.wallpaperflare.com/wallpaper/39/420/874/birds-design-4k-green-wallpaper-preview.jpg"
              alt=""
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="page1half">
        <h1>Did you know that we can make a difference in food waste?</h1>
        <h1>
          Guess What,the <b style="color: rgb(160, 237, 37);">FoodForward</b> lets you save unsold food in your favourite
          restaurants from being thrown away
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div id="page2">
        <div id="scroll">
          <h1>
            "Did you know that approximately one-third of all food produced globally goes to waste? That's over 1.3 billion tons of food wasted each year, while millions around the world suffer from hunger and malnutrition."
          </h1>
        </div>
        <img src="../images/donate.jpg" alt="" />
      </div>
      <div id="part2half">
        <h1>Our Partners</h1>
        <div class="people" id="people"></div>
      </div>
      <div id="page3">
        <div id="cards_1">
        <div class="testimonial-container">
          <div class="testimonial-header">
            <div class="testimonial-avatar"></div>
            <div>
              <div class="testimonial-name">largest FSN platform</div>
              <div class="testimonial-company">FastForward is the largest FSN</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-text">
            "Currently , FoodForward is the largest FSN , which is distributing over 10-12 Tons of left-over food to restaurants"
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-container">
          <div class="testimonial-header">
            <div class="testimonial-avatar"></div>
            <div>
              <div class="testimonial-name">1500+ restaurants</div>
              <div class="testimonial-company">donation average : 4 tons </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-text">
            "More than 1500 restaurants are partnered and serving around 10,000-15000 needy ones."
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-container">
          <div class="testimonial-header">
            <div class="testimonial-avatar"></div>
            <div>
              <div class="testimonial-name">10,000,000+ meals served</div>
              <div class="testimonial-company">and still counting....</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-text">
            "FoodForward has helped in provind a total of 10,000,000 meals till the establishment."
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-container">
          <div class="testimonial-header">
            <div class="testimonial-avatar"></div>
            <div>
              <div class="testimonial-name">Labour reduction</div>
              <div class="testimonial-company">around 4000 workers lessens</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-text">
            "Since the food which was about to be wated is now being distributed so it results in reduced garbage ."
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
      <footer>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="left">
            <h2>Subscribe to Our Emails</h2>
            <p>
              Stay up to date with the latest at Feed the Need Missions,
              delivered right to your inbox. Sign up below to subscribe to our
              newsletter and email updates.
            </p>
            <form action="#" method="POST">
              <div class="input-group">
                <input
                  type="email"
                  name="email"
                  placeholder="Email Address*"
                  required
                />
                <button type="submit">Subscribe</button>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
          <div class="middle">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="#">Weekly Sites</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Disaster Relief</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Employment</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Blog</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Contact Us</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="right">
            <h2>Get Involved</h2>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="#">Donate Now</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Volunteer</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Events</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Give Back Beef</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Table Talk</a></li>
              <li><a href="#">Gobble Kits</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/gsap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/ScrollTrigger.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/locomotive-scroll@3.5.4/dist/locomotive-scroll.js"></script>
    <script>
      var home = document.querySelector("#nav #navpart-2 #home");
      var about = document.querySelector("#nav #navpart-2 #about");
      function redirectToAbout() {
        window.location.href = "/about";
      }
      function redirectToHome() {
        window.location.href = "/";
      }
      function redirectToDonate() {
        window.location.href = "/donate";
      }
      function redirectToContact() {
        window.location.href = "/contact";
      }
      function redirectToFeeding() {
        window.location.href = "/feeding";
      }
      function redirectToMilestone() {
        window.location.href = "/milestone";
      }
      function redirectToPartner() {
        window.location.href = "/partner";
      }
    </script>
    <script src="../javascripts/script.js"></script>
 </body>
</html>
